astapi, uvicorn, playwright, boto3\n│   └── main.py                # FastAPI service, POST /execute, GET /health\n├── worker/                    # Phase 2: Cloudflare Worker + DO\n│   ├── wrangler.toml          # Worker config\n│   ├── package.json\n│   ├── .env                   # CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID, CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN\n│   └── src/\n│       ├── index.ts           # Worker entry: routing, auth, WebSocket→DO\n│       └── agent-session.ts   # AgentSession DO: ReAct loop, LLM calls, tool execution\n├── agents-website/app/        # Phase 4: React frontend\n│   ├── wrangler.toml          # Pages config (name=cf-agent-web)\n│   └── src/\n│       ├── App.tsx             # Routes: /, /login, /dashboard\n│       ├── lib/api.ts          # API_BASE, WS_BASE constants\n│       └── pages/\n│           ├── Home.tsx        # Landing page (cleaned)\n│           ├── Login.tsx       # Auth page\n│           └── Dashboard.tsx   # Main app (cleaned)\n└── agent227                   # Unknown file, existed before project\n```\n\n### Key Configuration\n- Cloudflare Account ID: `846663c4c93fe5665f3b727025f534c9`\n- CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN: `aGbYCg2ubrE3JKi-iLAtNJKQKvRfvJEmwDue3Lxz`\n- AI Gateway Token (CF_AIG_TOKEN secret): `AlBHz4QhE-wo2nHcyEKJGX6dO_uofy67-kbXJ0t3`\n- AI Gateway base: `https://gateway.ai.cloudflare.com/v1/846663c4c93fe5665f3b727025f534c9/cf-agent-gateway/compat`\n- AI Model: `workers-ai/@cf/zai-org/glm-4.7-flash`\n- R2 Endpoint: `https://846663c4c93fe5665f3b727025f534c9.r2.cloudflarestorage.com`\n- R2 Bucket: `sandbox`\n- R2 AK: `4d4316dd9b601ec9a03d9ee901e979c1`\n- R2 SK: `3d15e02de6fdda57daa2ab4810afc0f752fdce7c00318020584f4f0b87e2f20b`\n- Worker URL: `https://cf-agent.liubowen1573-846.workers.dev`\n- Pages project: `cf-agent-web`\n- API base in frontend: `https://api.agents.cloudc.top` / `wss://api.agents.cloudc.top`\n\n### Naming Conventions\n| Component | Name |\n|-----------|------|\n| Worker | `cf-agent` |\n| DO class | `AgentSession` |\n| DO binding | `AGENT_SESSION` |\n| R2 Bucket | `sandbox` |\n| Docker container | `cf-sandbox` |\n| Pages project | `cf-agent-web` |\n| AI Gateway | `cf-agent-gateway` |\n\n### Agent Session DO Key Design\n- WebSocket messages: `{type: \"task\", content: string, task_id: string}`\n- DO Storage keys: `task:{taskId}:messages`, `task:{taskId}:steps`\n- WebSocket push types: `status`, `reasoning`, `thinking`, `action`, `screenshot`, `answer`, `error`\n- DO ID format: `{userId}:{taskId}` (from index.ts routing)\n- System prompt includes Plan→Reason→Act→Observe workflow instruction\n- Tools defined: only `navigate(url)` currently\n- MAX_STEPS configurable via env var (default 10)\n- LLM response field `reasoning_content` is pushed as `reasoning` type (glm model provides this)\n- LLM response field `content` (when tool_calls present) pushed as `thinking` type\n\n### Frontend WebSocket Message Handling\n```\nstatus    → plain log\nreasoning → 🧠 prefix\nthinking  → 💭 prefix\naction    → 🔧 prefix\nscreenshot → 📸 prefix\nanswer    → ✅ prefix, sets status=completed\nerror     → ❌ prefix, sets status=failed\n```\n\n### Deploy Commands\n```bash\n# Worker\ncd /home/ubuntu/cf-agent/worker && CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=aGbYCg2ubrE3JKi-iLAtNJKQKvRfvJEmwDue3Lxz npx wrangler deploy\n\n# Pages\ncd /home/ubuntu/cf-agent/agents-website/app && CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=aGbYCg2ubrE3JKi-iLAtNJKQKvRfvJEmwDue3Lxz npx wrangler pages deploy --branch=production\n\n# Sandbox rebuild\ncd /home/ubuntu/cf-agent/sandbox && docker stop cf-sandbox && docker rm cf-sandbox && docker build -q -t cf-sandbox . && docker run -d --name cf-sandbox -p 9090:9090 -e R2_ENDPOINT=\"https://846663c4c93fe5665f3b727025f534c9.r2.cloudflarestorage.com\" -e R2_ACCESS_KEY=\"4d4316dd9b601ec9a03d9ee901e979c1\" -e R2_SECRET_KEY=\"3d15e02de6fdda57daa2ab4810afc0f752fdce7c00318020584f4f0b87e2f20b\" -e R2_BUCKET=\"sandbox\" cf-sandbox\n```\n\n## TOOLS EXECUTED\n- SSH connected to EC2, copied task.md\n- Created sandbox/ with Dockerfile, requirements.txt, main.py\n-